## Controles Implementados

### Rate Limiting
```yaml
rate_limits:
  per_minute: 100
  per_hour: 1000
  burst: 10
```

### Timeout
```yaml
timeouts:
  default: 30s
  database: 60s
  external_api: 30s
  generation: 120s
```

### Isolamento
```yaml
tenant_isolation:
  enforce: true
  validate_on_each_call: true
  error_on_leak: true
```
